data.name: Southwest Chicken Bowl
data.quickTastyDescription: A hearty bowl filled with grilled chicken, black beans, corn, and fresh veggies, topped with a zesty dressing.
detailedCookingInstructions: Grill the chicken breast until cooked through and slice it into strips.
In a large bowl, combine the black beans, corn, cherry tomatoes, and diced avocado.
Add the grilled chicken on top of the veggie mix.
In a small bowl, whisk together lime juice, olive oil, cumin, chili powder, salt, and pepper to create a dressing.
Drizzle the dressing over the bowl and toss gently to combine.
Garnish with fresh cilantro before serving.
data.detailedName: Southwest Chicken Bowl with Grilled Chicken, Black Beans, and Corn
data.modifiersForBase: Add black beans and corn for a southwestern twist
